title: The Perfect Fall Sandwich
summary: The Perfect Fall Sandwich might be just the main course you are searching for. This recipe serves 2 and costs $1.93 per serving. One portion of this dish contains around 24g of protein, 19g of fat, and a total of 464 calories. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes roughly 5 minutes. It can be enjoyed any time, but it is especially good for Autumn. 74 people have made this recipe and would make it again. If you have apple butter, baguette, gruyere, and a few other ingredients on hand, you can make it. To use up the apple butter you could follow this main course with the Apple Butter Pinwheel Cookies as a dessert. All things considered, we decided this recipe deserves a spoonacular score of 79%. This score is good. Try The Perfect Fall Grilled Cheese Sandwich, Fall Popcorn Balls with Reese’s Pieces: Perfect treat for fall parties, and Carrot Soup, perfect for fall for similar recipes.
